This is the ION resource files directory.

Resource files are used when the ION system, a capability container or an example is started.

Resource files may be placed in this directory by different repository owners, in order for them to be
available when the system is started. Place or edit files with care.


DIRECTORY STRUCTURE:

./apps/     App definition/configuration files (YML format and extension)

./config/   ION configuration files (YML format and extension). Example: pyon

./deploy/   Container startup (deploy) files (YML format and extension).

./launch/   CEI launch configurations

./preload/  Files used to preload resources into a fresh system

./profile/  Capability container profile definitions
